Package: fastEda
Type: Package
Title: A Collection of Functions to Run Fast Exploratory Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Arafath Hossain <a.h.fahad90@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Arafath Hossain <a.h.fahad90@gmail.com>
Description: `fastEda` is intended to make repeated plotting tasks easier and faster. 
    Using the available functions users will be able to quickly create multiple plots on similar data to perform common tasks such as:
    * Plot inidivdual feature/variable,
    * Visualize plots to explore bivariate relation between target feature and input features.
